org.apache.poi.util

Class CodePageUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.util.CodePageUtil

  • public class CodePageUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    Utilities for working with Microsoft CodePages.

    Provides constants for understanding numeric codepages, along with utilities to translate these into Java Character Sets.

    (用于使用Microsoft CodePages的实用程序。提供用于理解数字代码页的常数，以及将它们翻译成Java字符集的实用程序。)

      • codepageToEncoding

        public static java.lang.String codepageToEncoding(int codepage)
                                           throws java.io.UnsupportedEncodingException

        Turns a codepage number into the equivalent character encoding's name (in Java NIO canonical naming format).

        (将代码页号转换为等效字符编码的名称（采用Java NIO规范命名格式）。)
        Parameters:
        codepage - The codepage number(代码页-代码页号)
        Returns:
        The character encoding's name. If the codepage number is 65001, the encoding name is "UTF-8". All other positive numbers are mapped to their Java NIO names, normally either "windows-" followed by the number, eg "windows-1251", or "cp" followed by the number, e.g. if the codepage number is 1252 the returned character encoding name will be "cp1252".(字符编码的名称。如果代码页号为65001，则编码名称为“UTF-8”。所有其他正值都映射到它们的Java NIO名称，通常是“Windows-”后面跟着数字，例如“Windows-1251”，或者“cp”后面跟着数字，例如如果代码页号是1252，则返回的字符编码名称将是“cp 1252”。)
        Throws:
        java.io.UnsupportedEncodingException - if the specified codepage is less than zero.(java.io. UnspectedEnCodingResponse-如果指定的代码页小于零。)

      • codepageToEncoding

        public static java.lang.String codepageToEncoding(int codepage,
                                                  boolean javaLangFormat)
                                           throws java.io.UnsupportedEncodingException

        Turns a codepage number into the equivalent character encoding's name, in either Java NIO or Java Lang canonical naming.

        (使用Java NIO或Java Lang规范命名将代码页编号转换为等效字符编码的名称。)
        Parameters:
        codepage - The codepage number(代码页-代码页号)
        javaLangFormat - Should Java Lang or Java NIO naming be used?(javaLangFormat -应该使用Java Lang还是Java NIO命名？)
        Returns:
        The character encoding's name, in either Java Lang format (eg Cp1251, ISO8859_5) or Java NIO format (eg windows-1252, ISO-8859-9)(字符编码的名称，采用Java Lang格式（例如Cp 1251，ISO 8859_5）或Java NIO格式（例如Windows-1252，ISO-8859-9）)
        Throws:
        java.io.UnsupportedEncodingException - if the specified codepage is less than zero.(java.io. UnspectedEnCodingResponse-如果指定的代码页小于零。)
        See Also:
        Supported Encodings
